data.description: Welcome to this spacious and versatile 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath pool home located within the sought-after Walden Lakes community in the heart of Plant City. Boasting ample living space and an ideal location, this property presents a unique opportunity to create your dream home. It's important to note that this property does require work and updates, making it an ideal canvas for those with a vision for customization and design. Whether you're an investor looking for a rewarding renovation project or a homeowner ready to put your personal touch on a home, this is an opportunity not to be missed. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of the Walden Lakes community and transform this property into a truly remarkable home. Contact us today to schedule a showing and unlock the potential of this gem in Plant City!
